Tactical Equipment





DroneDefender™
DroneDefender is a directed-energy unmanned aircraft system countermeasure. It quickly disrupts the adversary's control of the drone, neutralizing it so that no remote action can occur.
Learn More 

More Tactical Equipment 





Supply Chain Assurance





Battelle Barricade™
Keep clone or counterfeit electronic components out of your supply chain. Battelle Barricade™ provides fast, economical and nondestructive authentication of integrated circuits and microchips from both trusted and untrusted sources. 
