Doing Business with UsWe know it can be difficult - and sometimes downright frustrating - to understand how to work with large organizations. At Battelle, we never want our clients, prospective clients or those we partner with as suppliers to feel that way about our company. Learn more below about how you can do business with Battelle.




 




Government ClientsFrom homeland security to public health, Battelle works with agencies in all sectors of the U.S. government - including the Department of Defense, Department of Homeland Security, Department of Energy, Environmental Protection Agency, National Institutes of Health, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, and Food and Drug Administration - as well as local and state agencies. View the full list of our contract vehicles.





Commercial ClientsThrough our innovative research and scientific rigor, Battelle helps commercial clients across a wide range of industries solve the challenges of today and tomorrow. Whether you are in manufacturing, a healthcare provider, a financial institution or a power company, we can offer innovative technology solutions that help your company grow. Contact us today to see how our cross-functional teams can help with your commercial challenges.

 






 




SuppliersWhether you are a small or disadvantaged business or a General Services Administration (GSA) contractor, Battelle aims to put together teams that can deliver outstanding results to our clients. Together, we can compete for projects we might not qualify for individually. Our clients benefit by being able to purchase a total solution and avoiding multiple contract vehicles with disparate contractors. Visit the Suppliers page for details on everything from invoicing to registration in our database.


        
  

 

